      <wp_comment_content><![CDATA[Cool postacard! Very simple but very nice too. I got one yesterday morning when I went to a post office to pick up two packages. Tomorrow I'm going to get two more packages so I hope there is at least one more postcard waiting for me :)

Thanks a lot for sending me all the stuff I have been ordering recently. My CrimethInc. distro here in Prague, the Czech Republic, is getting bigger every day. I send books and journals and some free stuff to people form my country almost every day and all this is possible only thanks to you fellas.

Tomorrow evening starts a mini-tour of one vegan sxe polit Czech band called Nidal. We are going to hit our country and Slovakia and I as a roadie will have a small polit distro on every single show. Mainly CrimethInc. stuff.

We are still working on a translation of DOWNOL which we hope to publish this year in the Czech language and other CWC stuff is going to be translated soon too.

Our CrimethInc. cell is called "IdeozloCin" which means "idea, crime, action" or  "crimethink in action" in Czech. Our website is under construction but we have at least a myspace profile - http://www.myspace.com/ideozlocin - it's all in Czech but at least you can check the profile to see that things are really happening here :)

Keep up the good fight!!!

xVeganLove666x
info@ideozlocin.cz
CrimethInc.CZ/SK aka IdeozloCin]]></wp_comment_content>
